text: The Mercedes-Benz EQ series is a series of electric vehicles. The series includes every Mercedes-Benz car that starts with 'EQ'. ==Models== ===SUVs=== The SUVs are the Mercedes-Benz EQA, Mercedes-Benz EQB, Mercedes-Benz EQC, Mercedes-Benz EQE SUV and the Mercedes-Benz EQS SUV. ===Sedans=== The sedans/saloons are the Mercedes-Benz EQE and the EQS. title: Mercedes-Benz EQ Series
